nodes.long_description:
🗺️ Not sure where to start your workout? T-ON FITNESS has your back!

We’ll build your training program for you—automatically!

Just follow along with our adorable characters…

 (it starts out easy, but… you’ll feel the burn)

💪 Fun? Yes. Sweaty? Also yes.

Enjoy yourself, but expect to sweat.
You’ll feel the change in your body.

“How hard could this be?” Oh, it’s hard.

(Our fitness expert says workouts should be tough 😂)

🌟 Build a 30-minute-a-day habit

Create a routine for the last 30 minutes of your day.

Even without doing extra workouts, you’ll wake up feeling different.

(Yes, we’ve all heard this before—but seriously, it works!)

🧘 Give your brain a break with 5-minute meditation

Close your eyes. Sit still. Just five minutes.

Take a deep breath… and when you open your eyes, let yourself settle for a moment.

Even your dopamine-soaked digital brain needs a break.

(Yes, we know it sounds boring. The psychologist made us include this part!)

👇 Join us now on Discord!

https://discord.com/invite/as8yVmjJcC

- Instagram : https://www.instagram.com/t.on_official/


- Youtube : https://www.youtube.com/@official_tion

nodes.long_description:
🗺️ 運動、何から始めればいいか分からない？T-ON FITNESSにお任せ！

あなたにぴったりのトレーニングプログラムを自動で提供！

かわいいキャラクターと一緒に動いてみてください…

（最初は楽だけど、だんだんキツくなってきます）

💪 楽しいけど、汗はかきます。

楽しくプレイしながらも、しっかり汗をかける本格的な運動。

体の変化を実感できます。

「こんなので疲れるわけが…」はい、疲れます。

（運動はツラくなきゃダメって、うちのトレーナーが言ってました😂）

🌟 1日30分の習慣づくり

1日の終わりに30分だけ、自分の習慣を作ってみましょう。

他の運動をわざわざしなくても、朝の目覚めが変わります。

（よく聞くセリフだけど、本当に変わるんですってば！）

🧘 5分の瞑想で、脳にも休憩を。

目を閉じて、ただじっとしてみましょう。たった5分。

深く息を吸って…目を開けたら、ほんの少し我慢して呼吸を整えて。

スマホ漬けでデジタル・ドーパミンにまみれた脳も、きっとリセットされます。

（作った本人も「退屈かも」って思ってます。

でも心理の専門家に言われたので、やりましょう！）

👇 今すぐDiscordに参加！

https://discord.com/invite/as8yVmjJcC

- Homepage : https://www.tioncare.com/jn


- Instagram : https://www.instagram.com/t.on_official/


- Youtube : https://www.youtube.com/@official_tion

nodes.long_description:
🗺️ 운동 뭐부터 해야 할지 모를 땐! 티온 피트니스!! 

알아서 훈련 프로그램 제공! 

귀여운 캐릭터와 따라 하다 보면.. (슬슬 힘들어짐) 

💪 재미있게 즐기지만 땀이 납니다. 
땀이 나는 운동으로 몸의 변화를 느껴보세요.
 
이걸로 뭐 힘들겠어? 네. 힘듭니다. 

(우리 운동 전문가가 운동은 힘들어야 한대요😂) 

🌟 하루 30분 습관 만들기 

하루 마지막 30분 습관을 만들어봐요. 

굳이 따른 운동을 하지 않아도 아침이 달라집니다. 

(맨날 듣는 말이잖아요. 달라진다니깐요)

 🧘 5분 명상으로 뇌도 쉬게 해주세요. 

5분 명상을 눈을 감고 가만히 있어보세요. 

깊게 숨을 내쉬며 눈을 떴을 때 

잠시 인내심을 가지고 호흡을 가다듬으면 

디지털 도파민에 중독된 뇌도 잠시 쉬게 됩니다. 

(만든 저도 지루한 건 알아요 하래요 심리 전문가가!)

👇 지금 바로 디스코드에서 함께해요

https://discord.com/invite/as8yVmjJcC

- 홈페이지 : https://www.tioncare.com/


- 인스타그램 : https://www.instagram.com/t.on_official/


- Youtube : https://www.youtube.com/@official_tion

nodes.long_description:
▪ Adventure with T-ON Care
Your avatar syncs with you to exercise together.
Enjoy activity modes focused on running and turn-based stage modes according to the main scenario.

▪ Personalized Intensive Workout
Fitness
Fitness provides customized exercises by analyzing user exercise data collected through the avatar's personal training in the intensive workout mode.

▪ Healing Your Day
Meditation
Meditation offers visualized meditations that enhance relaxation and restfulness of the body after exercise.

▪ 15 Expert-Researched Exercise Movements
The 15 exercise movements included in the content are designed based on expert research.

▪ Say Goodbye to Boring Workouts,
Fun for Everyone, Young and Old
From T-ON Friends' dialogues to movement guides, rich BGM, and narration add to the fun of exercising.
